’Ů@71d7083346cd5ce8cd3410055591c2e7fb2884a842c0b7016745dc07a66c3be7ÚTitle: title: str join
Path: Examples
Content:
Create a string from input.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ['nu', 'shell'] | str join
nushell

```
Create a string from input with a separator.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ['nu', 'shell'] | str join '-'
nu-shell

```
